2484.name: GAME_SERVER_ID_UNIQUE_ID_NOT_LINKED
2484.short_description: The game server ID and title ID were not linked, or the request did not send a game server ID. This error should never happen normally.
2484.long_description: The game server ID and title ID were not linked, or the request did not send a game server ID. This error should never happen normally.
2484.short_solution: File a bug report with as much detail as possible at https://github.com/PretendoNetwork/account/issues/new.
2484.long_solution: File a bug report with as much detail as possible at https://github.com/PretendoNetwork/account/issues/new.
